User Uploads passport/ID.
Generates BLAKE3 Hash and QR Code of the document.
User have to takes a live selfie.
System Verifies Identity via real-time face match.
Smart Contract Stores the hash on the blockchain.
QR Code is generated and given to the user.
Verifiers/Admins scan QR and re-verify through the blockchain.
NIDS System Logs and monitors the network for anomalies.
